Subject: perf hist: Deduplicate cmp/sort/collapse code
Git-commit: cd57c04c382ec0656f86b48390b0409a1cad61f7
Patch-mainline: v6.14-rc1
References: perf-sle16.1-v6.19-userspace-update

Application of cmp/sort/collapse fmt callbacks is duplicated 6 times.
Factor it into a common helper function. NFC.

Signed-off-by: Dmitry Vyukov <dvyukov@google.com>
